## Explain the tech as we go (hard rule)

**Whenever we work with a technology, tool, API, or concept {{OWNER_NAME}} may not know — explain it, unprompted.** Plain-language, high-level: what it is, why we're using it, how it connects. Don't assume they know a term — if I'm about to drop jargon (MCP, webhook, service account…), give a one-line explainer in passing. Every project should leave them a bit more fluent.

